			<p class="g_16">{translate('Please specify a default "FROM" address and "SENDER" name below. It is recommended to use a FROM address like: <strong>admin@yourdomain.com</strong>. Some mail provider (e.g. <em>mail.com</em>) may reject mails with a FROM: address like <em>name@mail.com</em> sent via a foreign relay to avoid spam.<br /><br />The default values are only used if no other values are specified by LEPTON. If your server supports <acronym title="Simple mail transfer protocol">SMTP</acronym>, you may want use this option for outgoing mails.')}
			</p>
			<div class="clear"></div>
			<hr/>
			<div class="clear sp_clear"></div>
			<label for="fc_server_email" class="g_6">{translate('Default from mail')}:</label>
